source: http://www.modulabs.co.kr/RL_library/1705

1. sudo apt-get install python3-pip

(1) 기본설치
2. cd ~
3. git clone https://github.com/openai/gym
4. cd gym
5. sudo pip install -e . # minimal install

(2) 모두설치; https://github.com/openai/gym#installing-everything
2. cd ~
3. git clone https://github.com/openai/gym
4. cd gym
5. sudo apt-get install -y python-numpy python-dev cmake zlib1g-dev libjpeg-dev xvfb libav-tools xorg-dev python-opengl libboost-all-dev libsdl2-dev swig
6. sudo pip install -e .[all]
